node.text: 6 weeks ago I gave birth to this beautiful little baby boy ( swipe ) and even though it might seem that I’m already back in shape, it’s far from reality. This is why I’ve been posting more on YouTube lately to give a more realistic point of view of the process after giving birth. I’m very exited to start training again, tomorrow will be the first official workout. I know my stretch marks will never go away, but at this point I’m almost proud of them. Because they remind me what I got in return 😊, but besides that I’m super motivated to get the booty back 🦵🏼Follow my journey on YouTube: Sandra Prikker
